  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n      \t\t\t\t\t\u003cul\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli id=\"Entry1\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003ca name=\"entry\" id=\"EntryAnchor\"\u003eanchor\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/62/623e8fc433d7df47250c64c8a9686240.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\" title=\"Image rendering courtesy of MVRDV\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cimg srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/62/623e8fc433d7df47250c64c8a9686240.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/62/623e8fc433d7df47250c64c8a9686240.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/62/623e8fc433d7df47250c64c8a9686240.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\" src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/62/623e8fc433d7df47250c64c8a9686240.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" title=\"Image rendering courtesy of MVRDV\" alt=\"Image rendering courtesy of MVRDV\" width=\"514\" height=\"\"/\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eImage rendering courtesy of MVRDV\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eAdaptive reuse projects have lately become a growing presence in \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/firms/cover/327/mvrdv\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eMVRDV\u003c/a\u003e\u0026#39;s portfolio, with new projects in \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/firms/cover/327/mvrdv\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eBerlin\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/article/150386766/mvrdv-completes-transformation-of-communist-era-tirana-pyramid-monument-in-albania\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAlbania\u003c/a\u003e, and \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/article/150432626/mvrdv-transforms-19th-century-structure-into-new-multifunctional-nio-house-amsterdam-hq\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAmsterdam\u003c/a\u003e drawing it to the front of what is now a popular charge in the EU market and amongst its \u003ca href=\"https://bustler.net/news/8995/winning-european-parliament-redesign-seeks-to-minimize-carbon-emissions-through-reuse\" target=\"_blank\"\u003egovernments\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/article/150321230/it-s-high-time-for-an-adaptive-reuse-revolution-says-oliver-wainwright-and-everyone-else\" target=\"_blank\"\u003edesign critics\u003c/a\u003e. Another new example to highlight today is their forthcoming Heerlen Holy Water conversion in the Dutch countryside in collaboration with Zecc Architecten. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/f3/f3af0e19da65513dc40f874ad1ba1821.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x578\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/f3/f3af0e19da65513dc40f874ad1ba1821.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/f3/f3af0e19da65513dc40f874ad1ba1821.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/f3/f3af0e19da65513dc40f874ad1ba1821.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/f3/f3af0e19da65513dc40f874ad1ba1821.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage rendering courtesy of MVRDV\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/f4/f492f449795d17e730cf595b2c05018e.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x578\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/f4/f492f449795d17e730cf595b2c05018e.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/f4/f492f449795d17e730cf595b2c05018e.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/f4/f492f449795d17e730cf595b2c05018e.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/f4/f492f449795d17e730cf595b2c05018e.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage rendering courtesy of MVRDV\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eBy inserting a climatised public pool space into the landmarked St. Francis of Assisi Church, the firm completed a transformation that once again confers a social function onto the space. The design affords a unique kind of configurability thanks to an adjustable pool floor that can be raised to constitute a new space for intimate gatherings. A bar is also included in the program. Construction is expected to be completed at some point in 2027.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/51/51974ffe999d03c349534301d676f233.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x578\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/51/51974ffe999d03c349534301d676f233.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/51/51974ffe999d03c349534301d676f233.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://arc